title: Best of The Herd
itunes:title: Best of The Herd
description:
Colin likes what he's seen from Eagles QB Jalen Hurts in his second season as the starter and what he has in common with other elite players in the NFL. He defends the Green Bay Packers organization for their success over the years and the real reason they are struggling this season. He gives you his Blazing 5 picks for week 9 of the NFL season. Plus, Super Bowl champion Emmanuel Sanders joins the show to defend his former QB Jimmy Garoppolo from the criticisms he's faced since losing the Super Bowl to the Chiefs and Patrick Mahomes. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
